[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1131","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1131.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1488","title":"IBM Scalable POWERparallel (SP) 2.0 SDR 远程文件读取漏洞","description":"IBM Scalable POWERparallel (SP) 2.0 系统中的 sdrd 守护进程存在未授权文件读取漏洞。该守护进程作为系统数据仓库（SDR）的远程访问接口，未对客户端请求进行身份验证，导致远程攻击者无需任何认证即可通过网络向目标 sdrd 服务发送特制请求，读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞影响 IBM SP2 系统，攻击者利用难度较低，可导致敏感信息泄露，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1488"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:32.927","remediation":"升级 IBM SP2 系统软件至厂商已修复版本（如 2.1 及以上），或禁用 sdrd 服务。如无法升级，在防火墙层面限制对 sdrd 端口（默认 2132/TCP）的访问，仅允许受信任管理节点连接，并配置 TCP Wrappers 进行主机访问控制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/i-079a.shtml","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7217.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/371","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19297"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1131.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1687","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1687.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1055","title":"Microsoft Excel 97 工作表函数任意代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Excel 97 在调用工作表函数前未向用户发出安全警告，攻击者可通过构造包含恶意 CALL 函数的 XLS 文件诱导用户打开，利用 CALL 函数加载并执行恶意 DLL，从而在目标系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Excel 97 及后续兼容版本，攻击者可通过社会工程方式诱导受害者打开特制文档触发，无需身份认证。目前已存在公开利用代码，危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1055"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.767","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS98-018 提供的补丁程序，该补丁可通过 https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-018 获取。同时在 Excel 中将宏安全级别设置为\"高\"以阻止未签名的 CALL 函数执行，并建议升级到 Office 2000 及以上版本以彻底规避该问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/179","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-018","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1737","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1055.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1055","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1055.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1055.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1055.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cx75-p9pm-2q97/GHSA-cx75-p9pm-2q97.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_600_700.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-356.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1055.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1687.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1706","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1706.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1087","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 无点IP地址安全区域绕过漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4 在处理 URL 中的 32 位无点 IP 地址时存在解析逻辑缺陷，将点分十进制格式以外的纯数字 IP 地址误识别为主机名而非 IP 地址，导致浏览器错误地应用本地 Intranet 区域安全策略。远程攻击者可构造包含无点 IP 地址的恶意 URL，诱使用户访问后绕过正常的安全区隔离，从而执行未授权操作。该漏洞影响 Internet Explorer 4 及早期版本，增大了内网环境下的攻击面。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1087"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:41.647","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 5.0 或更高版本，或改用现代浏览器（如 Edge/Chrome/Firefox）。IE 4 已停止支持且不再接收安全更新，应彻底停止使用。无法升级时可配置代理服务器过滤包含纯数字 IP 的 URL 请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q168/6/17.asp","http://www.microsoft.com/Windows/Ie/security/dotless.asp","http://www.osvdb.org/7828","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-016","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2209","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1087.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1087","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1087.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1087.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1087.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9rv3-rxw8-xr7c/GHSA-9rv3-rxw8-xr7c.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000990.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1087.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--99ba35f8-d4eb-4aae-be83-0d60e01586a1.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1706.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1708","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1708.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1094","title":"微软 Internet Explorer MK协议缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4.01 及更早版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向用户发送包含特制长 URL 的链接（使用 \"mk:\" 协议）并诱使用户点击，触发缓冲区溢出，从而在用户系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响范围较广，攻击门槛较低，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1094"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:42.553","remediation":"安装 Microsoft KB Q176697 补丁，或将 Internet Explorer 升级至 4.01 Service Pack 1 及以上版本（如 IE 5.01 SP2）。对于现代系统，建议迁移至 Microsoft Edge 等受支持的浏览器，旧版 IE 已停止安全更新且不再接收补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88480839506155&w=2","http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q176/6/97.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/917","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1094.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1094","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1094.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1094.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1094.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wcrg-6ghq-6288/GHSA-wcrg-6ghq-6288.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88085/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1094.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000992.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1708.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1709","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1709.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1127","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 命名管道 RPC 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的命名管道 RPC 连接关闭机制存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过发送包含畸形数据的连接请求，导致系统无法正常关闭无效的命名管道 RPC 连接，从而引发资源耗尽型拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。微软已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1127"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:46.667","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS98-017 提供的补丁程序（KB195733）。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议升级至 Windows Server 2012 或更高版本。临时缓解措施：在防火墙层面阻止对 RPC 服务（TCP/UDP 135 端口）的匿名外部访问，并限制命名管道连接来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q195/7/33.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/523.php","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-017","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1127.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1127","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1127.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1127.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1127.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fjjp-8g8w-55f2/GHSA-fjjp-8g8w-55f2.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86274/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_600_700.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-772.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1709.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1800","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1800.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1233","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 域名解析访问限制漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 存在访问限制绕过漏洞。当用户发起初始会话请求且其 IP 地址无法反向解析为 DNS 域名时，IIS 未能正确限制该请求的访问权限，即所谓的\"域名解析\"漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过使用无法解析到 DNS 域名的 IP 地址发起初始会话请求，绕过访问控制策略，获取未授权访问。该漏洞影响 IIS 4.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1233"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:00.120","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-039 提供的 IIS 4.0 域限制热修复补丁（KB241562/KB241805），该补丁修正了 IIS 4.0 在 IP 地址无法解析为 DNS 域名时错误放行首次会话请求的问题。由于 IIS 4.0 及 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）并部署最新版 IIS。临时缓解措施：在 IIS 管理器中禁用基于域名的访问限制策略，改为使用 IP 地址范围限制；同时确保反向 DNS 解析服务正常工作，避免因解析失败导致访问绕过。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q241/5/62.asp","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/657","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-039","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3306","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1233.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1233","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1233.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1233.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-53c2-2qjx-38qh/GHSA-53c2-2qjx-38qh.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/1xxx/cve-1999-1233.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1233.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--f8160a66-e7e6-44ab-9c71-410f00677cdc.json","https://github.com/RiskBasedPrioritization/RiskBasedPrioritizationAnalysis/blob/3d5cc1819ecb8cbc3aeb75d9a8260318544faf56/data_in/acme/acme_cves.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1800.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1809","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1809.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1246","title":"Microsoft Site Server 3.0 Direct Mailer 明文密码存储漏洞","description":"Microsoft Site Server 3.0 的 Direct Mailer 功能将用户域名和密码以明文形式保存在 TMLBQueue 网络共享中，该共享目录默认权限设置不当，允许网络中的任意用户访问。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过网络共享读取存储的凭据信息，进而获取系统权限。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Site Server 3.0 版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1246"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:01.790","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft KB Q229972 安全更新以解决 Direct Mailer 明文存储密码问题。如无法安装更新，手动收紧 TMLBQueue 网络共享的 NTFS 权限，仅允许授权管理员账户访问，移除 Everyone/Anonymous 写入权限，并启用 SMB 签名防止中间人窃取。建议尽快迁移至受支持的邮件服务产品，Site Server 3.0 已停止技术支持，无法获得后续安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q229/9/72.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2068","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1246.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1246","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1246.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1246.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-99cm-v3cq-wf9j/GHSA-99cm-v3cq-wf9j.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1246.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87849/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--bcb834d4-2dd0-4c27-9456-4d8219890aab.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1809.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1888","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1888.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1293","title":"Apache HTTP Server 1.2.5 mod_proxy 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Apache HTTP Server 1.2.5 及更早版本中的 mod_proxy 模块存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的畸形 FTP 命令，触发 mod_proxy 模块在处理 FTP 代理请求时出现错误，导致 Apache 进程崩溃转储核心。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，影响运行 Apache 1.2.5 及之前版本的系统，攻击者可通过持续发送恶意请求造成服务不可用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1293"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:07.733","remediation":"升级至 Apache HTTP Server 1.3.x 或更高版本（1.2.5 及更早版本已停止维护）。如无法升级，在配置中禁用 mod_proxy 模块或限制代理请求来源 IP。同时建议迁移至当前主流版本（2.4.x）以获得持续安全支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88413292830649&w=2","http://www.apache.org/info/security_bulletin_1.2.5.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1293.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1293","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1293.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1293.json","https://github.com/zmerry/z-marvel.github.io/blob/581a79f0e7ceb8cdb3e444922154e004cca44bbb/vulbox/webvul/high/Apache%E7%9A%84mod_proxy%E6%8B%92%E7%BB%9D%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E(CVE-1999-1293).html","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/1xxx/cve-1999-1293.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/1999/CVE-1999-1293.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1888.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1900","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1900.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1324","title":"OpenVMS VAXstations 登录失败锁定机制绕过漏洞","description":"Open VMS VAXstations 5.3 至 5.5-2 版本中，当使用 VMS DECwindows 或 MOTIF 图形界面时，系统未能正确限制超过登录失败阈值的用户账户访问权限。具体而言，当用户账户因多次登录失败触发 break-in 限制后，系统并未实际禁用该账户，导致攻击者可以绕过账户锁定机制持续进行暴力破解密码攻击。该漏洞降低了暴力破解的难度，使远程攻击者更容易通过枚举方式获取系统访问权限，影响所有运行受影响版本 Open VMS 的 VAXstations 设备。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1324"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:11.863","remediation":"升级 Open VMS 至 5.5-3 或更高版本，该版本已修复登录失败阈值检测失效问题。如无法升级，在 SYLOGIN.COM 或系统登录脚本中增加登录失败计数检查逻辑，并启用 SYSGEN 参数 LGI_BRK_LIM 强制限制。同时配置 INTRUSION_RECORD 启用入侵检测记录，监控异常登录行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/d-06.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7225","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-1324.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1324.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1324","https://github.com/bb1nfosec/Information-Security-Tasks/blob/14e2094f7bd96d2cb82493a9a6968ae7aa4fed5e/feeds/2026-06-07.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1324.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1324.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5r36-3w36-p2fp/GHSA-5r36-3w36-p2fp.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_200_300.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87872/info.html","https://github.com/jmohitz/SECAI/blob/33119e592f944e313664a5f75ae76284ea4b3fe8/data/CWE/307.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1900.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1982","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1982.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1512","title":"AMaViS 病毒扫描器远程代码执行漏洞","description":"AMaViS 病毒扫描器 0.2.0-pre4 及更早版本存在命令注入漏洞。远程攻击者可通过发送包含恶意 shell 元字符的感染邮件，并在 Reply-To 字段中嵌入系统命令，当 AMaViS 处理邮件时触发命令执行。由于 AMaViS 以 root 权限运行，攻击者可直接获取服务器完全控制权，造成严重安全威胁。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1512"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:35.963","remediation":"升级 AMaViS 至 0.3.0 及以上版本，该版本修复了 reply-to 字段的 shell 元字符过滤逻辑。如无法升级，在 sendmail/procmail 调用链中对邮件头部进行严格过滤，阻止包含 `;`、`|`、`` ` `` 等 shell 元字符的 reply-to 字段进入扫描流程，或改用 amavisd-new 替代旧版 AMaViS。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93219846414732&w=2","http://www.amavis.org/ChangeLog.txt","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/527","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2349"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1982.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0006","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0006.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0154","title":"Microsoft IIS 2.0/3.0 附加点号源码泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 2.0/3.0 存在源代码泄露漏洞，远程攻击者通过在 ASP 页面 URL 末尾附加一个点号（.），即可绕过服务器脚本执行机制，直接读取 ASP 文件的原始源代码，导致数据库连接字符串、业务逻辑等敏感信息暴露。该漏洞影响 IIS 2.0 及 3.0 版本，攻击无需认证，仅需发送特制 HTTP 请求即可触发，利用难度极低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0154"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"1999-12-31","remediation":"立即升级至 IIS 4.0 或更高版本（可通过 Windows NT 4.0 Option Pack 安装），该漏洞已在 IIS 4.0 及之后版本中修复。对于已停止支持的旧系统，应迁移至受支持的 Windows Server 版本并部署最新安全更新，同时在 IIS 中禁用不必要的脚本映射作为纵深防御。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0154","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20481","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0154.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0154.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0154","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0154.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0154.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0154.md","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0154.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0154.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80405/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0006.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0006.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0006.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0980","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0980.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1148","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 FTP 服务拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 及更早版本中的 FTP 服务存在资源耗尽型拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过同时发起大量被动模式（PASV）连接请求，消耗服务器连接资源池，导致 FTP 服务无法响应正常用户请求，形成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 Option Pack 等预装 IIS 4.0 的系统，攻击复杂度低，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1148"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS98-006 提供的补丁程序，或升级至 Windows 2000 及以上版本操作系统（自带 IIS 5.0 及以上版本），以彻底修复该漏洞。对于仍运行 Windows NT 4.0 的系统，建议尽快迁移至受支持的操作系统版本并限制 FTP 匿名访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q189/2/62.ASP","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-006","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1215"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0980.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1033","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1033.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1294","title":"Microsoft Windows 3.51 Office Shortcut Bar 权限许可和访问控制漏洞","description":"Windows 3.51 系统中 Office 快捷工具栏（OSB）启用了备份和恢复权限，这些权限会被从快捷栏启动的文件管理器等程序继承，导致本地用户能够读取其本无权访问的文件夹。攻击者仅需以本地用户身份从 OSB 启动程序即可触发，影响系统文件夹的机密性。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1294"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议升级至 Windows NT 4.0 或更高版本，该问题已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，可修改注册表将 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Office\\ShortcutBar 中 BackupRestore 键值设为 0，或通过组策略限制本地用户从快捷栏启动文件管理器以阻断权限继承路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q146/6/04.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/562"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1033.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1044","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1044.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1328","title":"Red Hat Linux linuxconf 符号链接攻击漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 5.1 系统中 linuxconf 工具在 1.11.r11-rh3 之前版本存在安全漏洞，本地用户可通过符号链接攻击（symlink attack）覆盖任意系统文件，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞利用条件为拥有本地账户，攻击复杂度低，无需认证即可完全控制目标系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1328"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-07-16","remediation":"升级 linuxconf 至 1.11.r11-rh3 或更高版本，该版本修复了符号链接竞争条件问题。Red Hat 官方已发布 RH51 安全公告提供更新包，建议用户通过 Red Hat 官方渠道获取并安装补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T11:21:58.102130741+00:00","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90383955231511&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7232.php","http://www.osvdb.org/6068","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh51-errata-general.html#linuxconf"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1044.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1046","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1046.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1330","title":"Sleepycat db库 snprintf 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"db库（版本1.85.4）中的snprintf函数忽略了size参数，导致在使用该函数时无法正确限制缓冲区大小。攻击者可利用此漏洞触发缓冲区溢出，造成信息泄露、权限提升或拒绝服务等危害。攻击者需要本地访问权限，且攻击复杂度较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1330"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议升级db库至1.85.4之后的版本，或应用Red Hat提供的RH42 errata补丁。对于使用db库的应用程序，应避免使用存在缺陷的snprintf实现，改用正确检查size参数的snprintf实现。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T11:35:31.598835092+00:00","references":["http://lists.openresources.com/Debian/debian-bugs-closed/msg00581.html","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602661419259&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7244.php","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh42-errata-general.html#db"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1046.toml"}]